HEADWORD: Inveiglement
<hw>In*vei"gle*ment</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act of
inveigling, or the state of being inveigled; that which inveigles;
enticement; seduction.</def> <rj><au>South.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
